{"settings":"{
	"todo-tree.tree.showScanModeButton": false,
	"workbench.iconTheme": "material-icon-theme",
	"bracket-pair-colorizer-2.activeScopeCSS": [
		"borderStyle : solid",
		"borderWidth : 1px",
		"borderColor : {color}",
		"opacity: 0.5"
	],
	"bracket-pair-colorizer-2.colors": [
		"Orange",
		"Orchid",
		"LightSkyBlue"
	],
	"dart.flutterSdkPath": "/Users/chris/Coding/flutter",
	"prettier.useTabs": true,
	"prettier.vueIndentScriptAndStyle": true,
	"auto-close-tag.activationOnLanguage": [
		"xml",
		"php",
		"blade",
		"ejs",
		"jinja",
		"javascript",
		"javascriptreact",
		"typescript",
		"typescriptreact",
		"plaintext",
		"markdown",
		"vue",
		"liquid",
		"erb",
		"lang-cfml",
		"cfml",
		"HTML (EEx)",
		"HTML (Eex)",
		"plist"
	],
	"window.zoomLevel": 0,
	"vetur.format.options.useTabs": true,
	"vetur.format.scriptInitialIndent": true,
	"vetur.format.styleInitialIndent": true,
	"eslint.format.enable": true,
	"[python]": {},
	"python.linting.pylintArgs": [
		"--load-plugins=pylint_django"
	],
	"git.confirmSync": false,
	"workbench.colorCustomizations": {
		"[Solarized Light]": {
			"editor.selectionHighlightBackground": "#e0e0e0"
		},
		"[Quiet Light]": {
			"editor.background": "#e4d4b8",
			"editor.lineHighlightBackground": "#d7c3a0"
		}
	},
	"dart.promptToGetPackages": false,
	"dart.env": {},
	"diffEditor.ignoreTrimWhitespace": false,
	"python.autoComplete.addBrackets": true,
	"code-runner.showExecutionMessage": false,
	"code-runner.showRunIconInEditorTitleMenu": false,
	"code-runner.showRunCommandInExplorerContextMenu": false,
	"code-runner.showRunCommandInEditorContextMenu": false,
	"code-runner.saveFileBeforeRun": true,
	"C_Cpp.updateChannel": "Insiders",
	"cSpell.userWords": [
		"Bioservo",
		"Ironhand",
		"MSDs",
		"WMSD",
		"gamified",
		"typeahead"
	],
	"files.exclude": {
		"**/.dart_tool": true,
		"**/.flutter-plugins": true,
		"**/.flutter-plugins-dependencies": true,
		"**/.metadata": true
	},
	"pasteImage.path": "${currentFileDir}/images",
	"editor.minimap.enabled": false,
	"cSpell.enabledLanguageIds": [
		"asciidoc",
		"c",
		"cpp",
		"csharp",
		"css",
		"git-commit",
		"go",
		"handlebars",
		"haskell",
		"html",
		"jade",
		"java",
		"javascript",
		"javascriptreact",
		"json",
		"jsonc",
		"latex",
		"less",
		"markdown",
		"php",
		"plaintext",
		"python",
		"pug",
		"restructuredtext",
		"rust",
		"scala",
		"scss",
		"text",
		"typescript",
		"typescriptreact",
		"yml"
	],
	"vscodeGoogleTranslate.preferredLanguage": "English",
	"markdown.extension.tableFormatter.enabled": false,
	"multiline-move.noLines": 5,
	"debug.openDebug": "neverOpen",
	"editor.wordWrapColumn": 80,
	"editor.wordBasedSuggestions": false,
	"[markdown]": {
		"editor.wordWrap": "on",
		"editor.wordWrapColumn": 80
	},
	"zenMode.fullScreen": false,
	"prettier.disableLanguages": [
		"markdown"
	],
	"gutterpreview.imagePreviewMaxHeight": 200,
	"zenMode.centerLayout": false,
	"editor.renderWhitespace": "none",
	"workbench.activityBar.visible": true,
	"workbench.statusBar.visible": true,
	"gitlens.mode.active": "zen",
	"customizeUI.stylesheet": {
		".editor-actions": "display: none !important;"
	},
	"editor.cursorBlinking": "solid",
	"zenMode.hideTabs": false,
	"dart.warnWhenEditingFilesOutsideWorkspace": false,
	"workbench.colorTheme": "Solarized Dark",
	"markdown-pdf.displayHeaderFooter": false,
	"vscodeGoogleTranslate.HoverTranslations": true,
	"cSpell.enabled": false,
	"gitlens.statusBar.reduceFlicker": true,
	"dart.debugExternalLibraries": false,
	"dart.debugSdkLibraries": false,
	"[vue]": {
		"editor.defaultFormatter": "dbaeumer.vscode-eslint"
	},
	"[html]": {
		"editor.defaultFormatter": "esbenp.prettier-vscode"
	},
	"terminal.integrated.shell.windows": "C:\\Windows\\System32\\cmd.exe",
	"terminal.integrated.shellArgs.windows": [
		"/K",
		"C:\\Users\\Chris\\Documents\\cmder\\vendor\\init.bat"
	],
	"[dart]": {
		"editor.formatOnSave": true,
		"editor.formatOnType": true,
		"editor.rulers": [
			80
		],
		"editor.selectionHighlight": false,
		"editor.suggest.snippetsPreventQuickSuggestions": false,
		"editor.suggestSelection": "first",
		"editor.tabCompletion": "onlySnippets",
		"editor.wordBasedSuggestions": false
	},
	"dart.analysisServerFolding": false,
	"dartImport.fixOnSave": true,
	"explorer.confirmDelete": false,
	"editor.formatOnSave": true
}"}
